### Получение токена (Password Grant)
POST http://localhost:8081/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Accept: application/json

grant_type=password&client_id=frontend&client_secret=my-super-secret-123&username=flaaim@list.ru&password=12345678



### Обновление токена через JSON
POST http://localhost:8081/token
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "grant_type": "refresh_token",
    "client_id": "frontend",
    "client_secret": "my-super-secret-123",
    "refresh_token": ""
}

